Spell:Shadow of Fate

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search
This Image Stub needs an Animation.
Shadow of Fate
Spell Information
School
Pip Cost5
Shadow Pip Cost1
Accuracy85%
Type /  / 
PvPNo
Spell Description
Deals 520 Balance Damage and 520 random School Damage to target and applies a +25% Balance Damage Global. Removes a harmful Ward from target or stores +5% max Health Damage each Round for three Rounds. Deals stored Damage to caster after three Rounds
File:(Spell Animation) Shadow of Fate.gif
Shadow of Fate Spell Animation
Training Sources
Training Points can purchase this Spell
Trainer
  • Trickster (Level 100+ Required)
Shadow of Fate Spellements cannot be used to learn this Spell
Requirements to Train
No Spells are required in order to train Shadow of Fate
Prerequisite to Train
No Spells require Shadow of Fate to be trained
